    <section xml:id="ChromaticPreDominantChords">
        <title>Chromatic Pre-Dominant Chords</title>
        <p>The table below shows how our study of chromatic harmonies in recent chapters includes the chromatic expansion of the pre-dominant <xref ref="HarmonicFlowchart" text="custom">harmonic function</xref> category.</p>
        <table>
            <title/>
            <tabular halign="center" top="major" bottom="minor" left="minor" right="minor">
                <row bottom="medium">
                    <cell>Ton.</cell>
                    <cell>Ton. Prol.</cell>
                    <cell>Pre-Dom.</cell>
                    <cell>Dom.</cell>
                    <cell>Ton.</cell>
